dcterms:creator: Michael Harries
dcterms:description: The ELEC2 dataset holds information on the Australian New South Wales (NSW) Electricity Market, containing 27552 records dated from May 1996 to December 1998, each referring to a period of 30 minutes. These records have 5 fields: a binary class label Y and four covariates X1, X2, X3, and X4 capturing different aspects of electricity demand and supply.
dcterms:title: ELEC2 dataset
